CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1776280294
OL,3,CChannel Islanders stopped when
OL,4,Creturning home after new E-Visa system
OL,5,Cintroduced
OL,7,FChannel Islanders returning from their
OL,8,Fholidays have been forced to pay for
OL,9,Fan emergency Electronic Travel
OL,10,FAuthorisation (ETA) visa after being
OL,11,Fdenied boarding at international
OL,12,Fairports.
OL,14,FThe disruption comes after the Crown
OL,15,FDependencies have not yet moved to a
OL,16,Fdigital permission system, known as
OL,17,Fthe Electronic Travel Authorisation,
OL,18,Fwhich the UK introduced in February
OL,19,F2026.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/14
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1776280294
OL,3,CChannel Islanders stopped when
OL,4,Creturning home after new E-Visa system
OL,5,Cintroduced
OL,7,FIt means physical documents and
OL,8,Fpassport stamps issued to Channel
OL,9,FIslanders are not always recognised.
OL,11,FAnna Kamiska, who has lived in Jersey
OL,12,Ffor eight years, was prevented from
OL,13,Fboarding her flight back home to the
OL,14,Fisland from Greece.
OL,16,FShe says: "I was very stressed, so I
OL,17,Fbought a speed ETA because people were
OL,18,Falready boarding the plane, which
OL,19,Falmost cost me #170, which is a
OL,20,Fshocking amount for me.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/14
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1776280294
OL,3,CChannel Islanders stopped when
OL,4,Creturning home after new E-Visa system
OL,5,Cintroduced
OL,7,F"I felt stressed, angry, upset, and
OL,8,Fpeople were looking at me like I was
OL,9,Fillegally trying to get to the UK."
OL,11,FAs of Wednesday 25 February, the UK
OL,12,Fgovernment stated that visitors
OL,13,Fwithout a digital permission, known as
OL,14,Fan ETA, will not be able to board
OL,15,Ftheir transport and cannot travel to
OL,16,Fthe UK.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/14
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1776280294
OL,3,CChannel Islanders stopped when
OL,4,Creturning home after new E-Visa system
OL,5,Cintroduced
OL,7,FThe rules stated that those travelling
OL,8,Ffrom Ireland, Guernsey, Jersey, or the
OL,9,FIsle of Man - as well as those with
OL,10,Fsettled status in the UK or right of
OL,11,Fabode - would not need an ETA.
OL,13,FHowever, Jersey, Guernsey, and the
OL,14,FIsle of Man are still issuing physical
OL,15,Fdocuments, instead of digital
OL,16,Fpermissions, which some overseas
OL,17,Fairline staff do not accept as valid
OL,18,Fwhen returning home.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/14
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1776280294
OL,3,CChannel Islanders stopped when
OL,4,Creturning home after new E-Visa system
OL,5,Cintroduced
OL,7,FAnna's cousin contacted her before her
OL,8,Fflight, warning her that people were
OL,9,Fgetting stopped and claiming they were
OL,10,Funable to board their flights.
OL,12,FAnna says that out of fear, she then
OL,13,Femailed Jersey Customs to check she
OL,14,Fhad the correct documents.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/14
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1776280294
OL,3,CChannel Islanders stopped when
OL,4,Creturning home after new E-Visa system
OL,5,Cintroduced
OL,7,F"I got a quick reply saying everything
OL,8,Fis fine, and so two days later, I went
OL,9,Fto the airport in Corfu, and they
OL,10,Fsaid, 'The UK doesn't see your status
OL,11,Fin Jersey, and unless you're going to
OL,12,Fbuy an ETA, we can't let you on the
OL,13,Fplane.'
OL,15,F"I was so shocked because I had
OL,16,Feverything. I even showed the staff
OL,17,Fthe emails, the documents saying I am
OL,18,Fliving in Jersey, and I have a
OL,19,Fsettlement status, and they still said
OL,20,Fno."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/14
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1776280294
OL,3,CChannel Islanders stopped when
OL,4,Creturning home after new E-Visa system
OL,5,Cintroduced
OL,7,FAnna says her friends are also fearful:
OL,9,F"Now my friends and colleagues who are
OL,10,Fon holiday are buying ETAs just in
OL,11,Fcase, because they are afraid they
OL,12,Fwill be stopped.
OL,14,F"It is so unfair, I feel punished for
OL,15,Fdoing everything correctly, having all
OL,16,Fthe correct documents. I have lived
OL,17,Fhere for eight years, and no one is
OL,18,Ftaking responsibility.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/14
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1776280294
OL,3,CChannel Islanders stopped when
OL,4,Creturning home after new E-Visa system
OL,5,Cintroduced
OL,7,F"What if I didn't have the time to buy
OL,8,Fthe ETA? I would have had to stay, pay
OL,9,Ffor accommodation and end up thousands
OL,10,Fof pounds less?
OL,12,F"It is very disappointing, we should
OL,13,Fbe able to go back to our home without
OL,14,Fany problems. We pay our taxes here,
OL,15,Fsome of my friends have mortgages
OL,16,Fhere, it is our home, we treat Jersey
OL,17,Fas home."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G8/14
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1776280294
OL,3,CChannel Islanders stopped when
OL,4,Creturning home after new E-Visa system
OL,5,Cintroduced
OL,7,FMagda Chmielewska, Honorary Polish
OL,8,FConsul of the Republic of Poland for
OL,9,FJersey, says it is an example of those
OL,10,Fpeople not born in the Channel Islands
OL,11,Fbeing treated differently.
OL,13,FShe explains: "We're treated like
OL,14,Fsecond-class citizens; it's
OL,15,Foutrageous. This is just another
OL,16,Fexample of discrimination.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G9/14
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38810
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1776280294
OL,3,CChannel Islanders stopped when
OL,4,Creturning home after new E-Visa system
OL,5,Cintroduced
OL,7,F"I have served in this role for over
OL,8,F14 years, and I have never felt so let
OL,9,Fdown. So do the community I serve, I
OL,10,Ffeel so little understood by people in
OL,11,Fpower.
OL,13,FA statement from Jersey Customs and
OL,14,FImmigration Service says: "We are
OL,15,Faware that some Jersey residents who
OL,16,Fhold EU Settlement Scheme (EUSS)
OL,17,Fstatus or other Jersey-issued
OL,18,Fimmigration permissions are being
OL,19,Frefused boarding by airlines and their
OL,20,Fimmigration status is not being
OL,21,Frecognised.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G10/14
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38811
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1776280294
OL,3,CChannel Islanders stopped when
OL,4,Creturning home after new E-Visa system
OL,5,Cintroduced
OL,7,F"We understand the impact this is
OL,8,Fhaving on those affected, and we are
OL,9,Fworking to resolve it.
OL,11,F"The documents which Jersey and the
OL,12,Fother Crown Dependencies issue are
OL,13,Ffully valid for entering the Common
OL,14,FTravel Area (CTA), and we are engaging
OL,15,Fclosely with airlines and carriers to
OL,16,Fmake this clear.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G11/14
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38812
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1776280294
OL,3,CChannel Islanders stopped when
OL,4,Creturning home after new E-Visa system
OL,5,Cintroduced
OL,7,F"This includes ensuring that airline
OL,8,Fstaff and border partners have
OL,9,Fdetailed instructions to prevent the
OL,10,Fissues being experienced by some
OL,11,Fpassengers.
OL,13,F"We are working with the UK Home
OL,14,FOffice, which has issued
OL,15,Fcommunications to carriers and
OL,16,Fhandling agents to make clear that
OL,17,FJersey-issued permissions are valid.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G12/14
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38813
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1776280294
OL,3,CChannel Islanders stopped when
OL,4,Creturning home after new E-Visa system
OL,5,Cintroduced
OL,7,F"We are currently working at pace to
OL,8,Fdigitalise permissions issued in
OL,9,FJersey. Digital permissions will
OL,10,Fbecome available in the Crown
OL,11,FDependencies in phases between June
OL,12,F2026 and early 2027.
OL,14,F"Until this time, the use of status
OL,15,Fletters, vignettes, and wet-ink stamps
OL,16,Fendorsed in the holder's passport will
OL,17,Fcontinue. "
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G13/14
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
